<div class="box before-box">
  <div class="small-12 hover-parent columns max-width">
    <div class="row icons top-space hover-inverse">
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-zip-o fa-4x"></div>
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-word-o fa-4x"></div>
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-pdf-o fa-4x"></div>
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-code-o fa-4x"></div>
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-video-o fa-4x"></div>
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-audio-o fa-4x"></div>
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-image-o fa-4x"></div>
      <div class="small-3 columns fa fa-file-text-o fa-4x"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="row text-left">
      <h1 class="font-a">INTRODUCING SQUIDL</h1>
      <h3 class="font-a subheader top-neg-space">A Tool For Getting Files from A to B</h3>
      <p class="text-left hover">Drag and Drop any file into this page to create a private link that you can share. All this without ever touching the cloud. Since Squidl is powered by Bittorrent, the more shares translates to a stronger and faster Squid.<br><br>

        Sign-up for Stats & Admin Control.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="box index-spinner hide">
  <i class="loadAnim fa fa-circle-o-notch fa-spin fa-5x fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i>
</div>

<div class="box after-box-uploading hide">
  <div class="row text-center p-excerpt">
    <div>
      <p>Share the link below and keep this window open. The file being shared only exists if at least 1 persons has 100% of the file. Members are able to delete links at will.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <input class="share-link" id="sharelink" type="text" value="http://placeholder" readonly>
      <button class="button btn-copy" data-clipboard-action="copy" data-clipboard-target="#sharelink">Copy</button>
    </div>

    <div>
      <ul class="inline-list">
        <li class="uploaded">0kb Uploaded</li>
        <li class="downloaded">0kb Downloaded</li>
        <li class="filesize">0kb Filesize</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
